---
title: Skillet Turkey Enchiladas with a Lime Radish Salad
description: For many cooks, ground turkey is something to make burgers with and not much else. So we’re hoping to expand everyone’s ground turkey repertoire with these enchiladas. The meat gets tossed with poblano pepper slices and wrapped in a tortilla shell before being smothered by a spiced tomato sauce and covered in cheese. We think it’s so good, you’ll be persuaded to make ground turkey a more regular part of your dinner rotation.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/turkey-enchiladas-6b4aa2dc.jpg
